These steel-toed boots of [[Mror|Mror Holds]] make are adorned with an embossed key on the toe. You can kick an object that contains a mundane or magical means of preventing access to cast the [[knock]] spell on it using the boots. Once this property of the boots has been used, they can't be used again in this way until the following dawn.